WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:00.280 --> 00:00:06.035
I was trying to show you all this beautiful little squirrel before I started.

00:00:06.035 --> 00:00:12.108
He's hungry; he's eating french fries.

00:00:12.108 --> 00:00:18.446
He grabbed that french fry and he's going up the tree.

00:00:18.446 --> 00:00:23.958
You see him up there?

00:00:23.958 --> 00:00:37.564
He's a fat thing; he likes french fries.

00:00:37.564 --> 00:00:39.182
God is so good.

00:00:39.182 --> 00:00:41.298
Don't you just love nature?

00:00:42.791 --> 00:00:45.715
I have a better angle.

00:00:45.715 --> 00:00:47.890
All right, let's see here.

00:00:47.890 --> 00:00:55.670
Well, we just came from Victory Church in Tulsa and we went to see John Bevere with my family.

00:00:55.670 --> 00:01:08.170
And you know, on the way to the church today, the Lord showed me that massive revival again and he spoke to me about being hungry.

00:01:08.425 --> 00:01:14.279
He said, 'Brandon, never lose your hunger for what's coming.

00:01:14.279 --> 00:01:25.820
' He said, 'You must remain hungry; keep yourself stirred up for what's coming, being filled with the Holy Spirit.

00:01:25.820 --> 00:01:34.800
' It's so vital to go and get in those rivers whenever you have a speaker come to your church like that.

00:01:35.320 --> 00:01:43.085
I've never visited Victory in Tulsa; we've always gone over to Collinsville.

00:01:43.085 --> 00:01:51.226
But when I was going over there, the Lord showed me the caps of the wells again and the great revival.

00:01:51.533 --> 00:01:55.959
He spoke to me and he said, 'Brandon, I'm going to use this church.

00:01:55.959 --> 00:02:00.700
' He's looking for people who will just say yes.

00:02:00.700 --> 00:02:05.885
He's looking for people because he said, 'Brandon, I'm running out of time.

00:02:05.885 --> 00:02:18.800
' There are so many ministers right now that he's tugging at their hearts; he's tugging at their heartstrings, saying, 'Will you be a vessel that will help me bring in the harvest?

00:02:18.800 --> 00:02:23.657
Will you be those people that God can use in this last outpouring?

00:02:23.657 --> 00:02:32.249
' There are so many people that if they just have a little bit of a check going, 'I don't know,' he's going to bypass you.

00:02:32.249 --> 00:02:49.840
He's out of time; he's not going to sit there and try to coerce you into being part of this revival.

00:02:55.971 --> 00:03:11.680
If you are a vessel that wants to be used in the revival, you're going to be used.

00:03:15.309 --> 00:03:22.626
I believe it's all hands on deck; this is an all-hands-on-deck type scenario.

00:03:22.626 --> 00:03:50.667
If your heart is hungry and thirsty for the Lord, get ready, because in this scenario, he is looking for those that seek him—they will find him.

00:03:50.667 --> 00:03:59.183
Those that knock, the door will be opened unto them.

00:03:59.183 --> 00:04:50.249
I'm telling you all, when I went into this church at Victory—and usually I steer away from megachurches a lot; I worked at one and I saw all the drama behind the scenes, you know, that's just my opinion—so Diana and I kind of gravitate towards smaller churches.

00:04:50.249 --> 00:05:19.676
But when we went in there, the presence of the Lord was so strong and the people going down to the altar worshipping the Father, it was genuine.

00:05:29.490 --> 00:05:29.835
You look for: is this a show?

00:05:41.840 --> 00:05:42.120
I always have my spiritual antennas up.

00:05:42.120 --> 00:05:46.933
When people say, 'Are you judging them?

00:05:46.933 --> 00:05:52.975
' No, I'm discerning.

00:05:55.740 --> 00:06:05.537
And I genuinely discerned a spiritual hunger in these people.

00:06:11.828 --> 00:06:30.240
The Lord showed me that it was about the Mabee Center and the glorious outpouring and the uncapping of the wells that were back in the 1950s.

00:06:31.453 --> 00:06:55.479
I told you, from Jack Coe to Oral Roberts to Kathryn Kuhlman to William Branham, to all the greats that used to walk in the healing movement and the revival—it was the same thing.

00:07:08.506 --> 00:07:10.320
I'm telling you, they barely touched a thimbleful of what God's about to do in these end times.

00:07:10.320 --> 00:07:23.295
We will finish this up, and he has called you for such a time as this.

00:07:23.295 --> 00:07:39.754
He saved the best for last; that's what he was showing me: 'Brandon, I've saved the best for last.

00:07:39.754 --> 00:08:06.509
' And right now, he said, 'I'm tugging at the people's hearts to see who is for me, who will go and preach the gospel to this final generation.

00:08:06.509 --> 00:08:18.110
' He said, 'Fan the flame of hunger; never lose the hunger for me.

00:08:18.110 --> 00:08:22.920
Keep me a priority in your life.

00:08:22.920 --> 00:08:47.672
' I just want to encourage you all to be excited about what God is about to do in this end-time army.

00:08:47.672 --> 00:08:58.080
Diana and I can see it; we both felt it.

00:08:58.080 --> 00:09:04.170
I said, 'My goodness, didn't you, babe?

00:09:04.170 --> 00:09:11.285
' It's amazing how hungry the people are.

00:09:11.285 --> 00:09:30.020
I really believe, tangibly, with Oral Roberts University being there and how hungry those kids are, you could see them there.

00:09:30.020 --> 00:09:35.222
Megan's handing in the to-go box.

00:09:35.222 --> 00:10:04.939
Bill Johnson is going to be there tonight and he's going to be preaching, and I've never heard him live before, so we're going to go listen.

00:10:16.640 --> 00:10:19.413
The old wells—so Bill Johnson's coming and he's going to preach three services, I believe.

00:10:19.413 --> 00:10:38.663
I've never heard him live before, so I thought, 'Well, let's go and check it out.

00:10:38.663 --> 00:10:47.537
' I guess he has Bethel Church out in California.

00:10:47.537 --> 00:10:53.270
I'm just hungry for y'all.

00:10:53.270 --> 00:11:08.578
I know what I've seen about the plague and the things that the Lord has told me about it.

00:11:11.986 --> 00:11:16.960
I made a video on it but I haven't released it.

00:11:16.960 --> 00:11:33.580
The Lord showed me more about this; I had an open-eyed vision about four days ago, and he showed me dates.

00:11:33.580 --> 00:11:57.760
I'm just keeping that to myself right now, just praying over it, because I don't want to be hasty in releasing something just because I see it.

00:11:57.760 --> 00:12:19.930
Because of how the platform has grown, I think it's wisdom to pray over things a lot more and not be so quick.

00:12:19.930 --> 00:12:27.440
Right now, he said, 'Fan the flame.

00:12:27.440 --> 00:12:34.966
Go on YouTube and fan the flame.

00:12:34.966 --> 00:12:45.399
Get people excited about what's coming—a major harvest of souls.

00:12:45.399 --> 00:12:51.330
' Look at all the things.

00:12:51.330 --> 00:13:10.313
In the first week of Trump being in office, all the change that is happening.

00:13:10.313 --> 00:13:13.900
Hasn't it been amazing, Diana?

00:13:13.900 --> 00:13:30.622
He's done more in the first week of his presidency than Joe Biden did in his whole four years.

00:13:30.622 --> 00:13:32.830
It's been incredible.

00:13:47.631 --> 00:13:49.325
Even with the Prince of Saudi Arabia—I started, I went, 'Oh my God, he's doing a deal with MBS.

00:13:49.325 --> 00:14:00.907
' He's like, 'I think we can make it a trillion-dollar deal.

00:14:00.907 --> 00:14:17.331
' It's just amazing to see the end times unfolding right in front of our faces.

00:14:28.565 --> 00:14:29.090
I believe we will see in the days ahead a great acceleration of Turkey helping out Syria.

00:14:29.090 --> 00:14:47.876
When I was praying, the Lord showed me that the Temple Mount, the Third Temple in Jerusalem, is about to be built.

00:14:47.876 --> 00:15:17.953
Trump will have a major part in bringing forth the peace accord with Saudi Arabia and these other nations, and we will see the Third Temple be built in a short amount of time.

00:15:17.953 --> 00:15:29.280
I'm not going to tell you when, but I'm telling you it's coming.

00:15:29.280 --> 00:15:42.880
Get ready, because we're seeing something that has to happen so that the Lord Jesus Christ is coming back.

00:15:44.131 --> 00:15:55.733
We're in that last generation; we are the generation that will not taste death.

00:15:55.733 --> 00:16:08.160
We are the generation that will experience the great outpouring, a spiritual awakening.

00:16:08.160 --> 00:16:15.972
Billie said, 'Brandon, it's bigger than a revival.

00:16:15.972 --> 00:16:24.560
' Because I said, 'A revival is coming, Mrs.

00:16:24.560 --> 00:16:25.400
Billie.

00:16:25.400 --> 00:16:36.370
' And she said, 'No, an awakening unto God is coming.

00:16:36.370 --> 00:16:54.880
' Billie said, 'An awakening unto God is a generation of people who are filled with and controlled by the Holy Spirit.

00:16:54.880 --> 00:17:08.780
' Diana's going to look that up for us so I can get it precise.

00:17:08.780 --> 00:17:13.815
Where did that squirrel go?

00:17:13.815 --> 00:17:24.009
Oh, he dropped the french fry on the limb up there.

00:17:24.009 --> 00:17:33.600
He's looking at me going, 'What is he doing down there?

00:17:33.600 --> 00:17:40.622
' He doesn't trust me; he's freaking out.

00:17:40.622 --> 00:17:47.702
Everybody want to say hi to Braden?

00:17:47.702 --> 00:17:52.305
There's my boy; that's Braden.

00:17:52.305 --> 00:18:02.083
He's the one that does the videos for you all the time.

00:18:02.083 --> 00:18:20.400
I'd show you my Paisley, but I still keep her secret right now because she's so young.

00:18:20.400 --> 00:18:26.800
Megan's in the back seat laying down.

00:18:26.800 --> 00:18:35.851
She just got her belly full of a hamburger.

00:18:35.851 --> 00:18:46.124
An awakening is when God sovereignly pours out his spirit and it impacts a culture.

00:19:01.464 --> 00:19:01.769
That is what happened during the Jesus Revolution.

00:19:01.769 --> 00:19:27.776
A revival, on the other hand, is what the church most experiences; it's when the church comes back to life and returns to passion.

00:19:27.776 --> 00:19:38.560
America needs a spiritual awakening, but the church needs a revival.

00:19:38.560 --> 00:19:42.400
It's a bigger impact.

00:19:54.183 --> 00:19:54.587
Just like she was talking about the Welsh Revival.

00:20:07.600 --> 00:20:42.320
In the Welsh Revival, they had to retrain the mules for the miners because they were so used to being spoken to with profanity that when the fire of God showed up and changed them, they had to retrain those donkeys because they didn't know how to do the commands without profanity.

00:21:00.265 --> 00:21:00.590
The revival changes you from the inside out.

00:21:01.951 --> 00:21:14.290
The Lord's going to change you from the inside out; he will deliver you from generational curses.

00:21:14.290 --> 00:21:24.180
Abraham was a father of many nations.

00:21:24.180 --> 00:21:30.880
It was a generational thing.

00:21:30.880 --> 00:22:00.840
What John Bevere said he called his rabbi friend, and his rabbi friend was telling him that it was 'I'll bless you,' and he repeats it three times in that Bible verse.

00:22:16.120 --> 00:22:16.555
It was generational, changing your bloodline in the spirit realm.

00:22:27.445 --> 00:22:32.591
We are changing what you thought—well, 'My dad was a drunkard, and his dad was a drunkard.

00:22:32.591 --> 00:22:39.799
' It will stop with me.

00:22:47.145 --> 00:22:50.666
I will be the one in my generation that will break the family curses.

00:22:50.666 --> 00:22:59.239
As for me and my house, we will serve the Lord.

00:22:59.239 --> 00:23:01.759
We're barrier breakers.

00:23:01.759 --> 00:23:13.429
I'm telling you, it's time to look up, for our redemption is drawing nigh.

00:23:13.429 --> 00:23:19.880
2025 will be a year of great outpouring.

00:23:19.880 --> 00:23:36.015
We're going to start to see a major turnaround starting, I believe, from Rosh Hashanah to Rosh Hashanah.

00:23:46.333 --> 00:23:51.620
The Lord said this to me: 'Brandon, we're going to start to see a major turnaround of things.

00:23:51.620 --> 00:24:09.462
' We see the first fruits of President Trump coming on the scene and changing things for the better.

00:24:09.462 --> 00:24:32.480
What the devil meant for bad, God's going to turn it around for good.

00:24:32.480 --> 00:25:03.200
In this next four years until the next Shmita cycle, we have a window to bring in the lost.

00:25:03.200 --> 00:25:31.987
Even if it's four years until the next Shmita cycle, we have a great opportunity to go home in the Rapture of the church by 2028.

00:25:31.987 --> 00:25:47.787
The Tribulation will kick off at the next Shmita cycle; it will be a seven-year window of tribulation.

00:25:48.533 --> 00:26:21.109
We would start to see this temple being built, like the Lord told me—that Trump would have a hand in bringing in the peace accord with Saudi Arabia so that they can build the Third Temple.

00:26:32.910 --> 00:26:33.145
What will we do with what God has given us?

00:26:33.145 --> 00:26:44.040
Especially you pastors: have a church ready for the Holy Spirit to move in.

00:26:44.040 --> 00:26:47.206
Are you all in?

00:26:47.206 --> 00:26:53.190
Have you said, 'Yes, Lord, here am I, use me'?

00:26:53.190 --> 00:27:04.240
Diana and I are saying, 'Yes, here am I, Lord, use us.

00:27:04.240 --> 00:27:06.947
' If he can use me, folks, he can use you.

00:27:15.924 --> 00:27:16.249
I was just a janitor.

00:27:16.249 --> 00:27:27.155
I cleaned floors for hours and I just said, 'God, use me.

00:27:27.155 --> 00:27:31.990
Send me to the nations.

00:27:31.990 --> 00:27:51.120
' Braden was a little boy; I'd sit him on my lap and we'd pray in the Holy Spirit.

00:27:51.120 --> 00:27:57.619
We have a compassion for the lost.

00:27:57.619 --> 00:28:05.222
He will do something with those that are hungry.

00:28:05.222 --> 00:28:08.709
Just sell out today.

00:28:08.709 --> 00:28:21.289
Never lose that childlike expectation, kind of like on Christmas morning, that Daddy's going to come through.

00:28:21.289 --> 00:28:29.550
He gives us an expected end; he has good things for us.

00:28:36.462 --> 00:28:45.071
I think a lot of times people get weary in well-doing and you lose that sense of awe, like John Bevere was talking about in his book today.

00:28:45.960 --> 00:28:54.297
Don't lose your awe for him because he's worthy of it all.

00:28:54.297 --> 00:29:04.925
All this other crap is just what it is.

00:29:04.925 --> 00:29:15.375
We just wanted to encourage y'all today.

00:29:35.620 --> 00:29:35.870
We were just sitting here looking at the squirrel.

00:29:36.120 --> 00:29:40.212
I saw the squirrel and his french fry he left up there.

00:29:40.212 --> 00:29:56.045
I wanted to be like Bob Ross and say, 'Hey, little peanut-in-the-pocket squirrel, how are you doing, little buddy?

00:29:56.045 --> 00:30:08.529
' We sit out here in the car because Megan doesn't like to get out much.

00:30:17.606 --> 00:30:25.835
We got Starlink up here, so we are able to do our internet and download our videos through our mobile command center.

00:30:25.835 --> 00:30:40.871
Braden got an Apple computer; we're so thankful for the person that sowed that to him.

00:30:40.871 --> 00:30:42.822
We're humbled.

00:30:42.822 --> 00:30:49.640
Never take for granted the small things.

00:30:49.640 --> 00:30:51.790
My heart's just full.

00:30:51.790 --> 00:31:00.060
We believe that Megan's going to be completely healed.

00:31:03.697 --> 00:31:09.080
You know, he said, 'Do you trust me?

00:31:09.080 --> 00:31:31.559
' If anything was to happen with Diana and me, it will help take care of her when we're gone.

00:31:31.559 --> 00:31:45.375
And those are the things we have to say: 'Do we trust him?

00:31:45.375 --> 00:32:07.729
' I say, 'Lord, I believe, but help my unbelief,' because right now I'm weak and having a hard time because I see my daughter is still overcoming.

00:32:07.907 --> 00:32:14.560
You can't let fear steal that peace.

00:32:14.560 --> 00:32:27.500
Diana doesn't have a problem with her weight; she's always Steady Eddie.

00:32:27.500 --> 00:32:34.337
Is our peanut-in-the-pocket squirrel up there again?

00:32:34.337 --> 00:32:43.657
He's looking at us like, 'Go away, dude.

00:32:43.657 --> 00:32:53.200
' Well, you can look around; there's a nice Olive Garden over there.

00:32:55.571 --> 00:33:01.540
Father, I thank you for every single one of these people.

00:33:09.919 --> 00:33:10.234
We call their marriages restored.

00:33:11.495 --> 00:33:15.186
We believe for babies, for supernatural childbirth.

00:33:21.839 --> 00:33:22.159
We believe for creative ideas for jobs.

00:33:22.159 --> 00:33:30.639
If you could like this video and subscribe.

00:33:43.520 --> 00:33:44.264
We have all these other channels—Portuguese, French, Hindi, Spanish, Korean, Chinese, Filipino, Russian, Vietnamese, and Japanese.

00:33:44.264 --> 00:33:48.679
It's all done through AI.

00:33:48.679 --> 00:34:01.234
He said, 'Minister to my people while it is day, for night is coming.

00:34:01.234 --> 00:34:14.600
' Put a smile on your face and a song on your heart.

00:34:14.600 --> 00:34:20.879
Jesus loves you so much.

00:34:34.422 --> 00:34:35.200
God bless you all, and we will see you again soon.

00:34:35.200 --> 00:34:35.919
Bye-bye.
